3>Importance of Space</h3>\r\nCreating a space for practice is so important.  The space allows you to explore your edges and to experiment with your abilities while ensuring that you protected.  It is true that you can practice yoga anyway and at anytime with little to no props.  Whether you practice on your carpet of your bedroom, your mat in the park or in the most soothing studio surrounded by props and essential oils, yoga will be there for you.\r\n<h3>Home Studio</h3>\r\nMy home studio provides enough space for 6 – 8 students practicing Hatha, Yin or Vinyasa, 2 students practicing yoga trapeze, or 8 – 10 practicing breathing.'),(528,545,'_content','field_62237ab93420b'),(529,545,'content_with_image_content','<h3><strong>Certifications</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>RYT 200 Yoga Certified Trainer (2016 Costa Rica)</li>\r\n 	<li>RYT 50 YB Naturals Yoga Trapeze Training (2017 Barcelona)</li>\r\n 	<li>RYT 50  Yin Yoga Training (2019 New York)</li>\r\n 	<li>RYT 50 Breath Coach Training (2019 Online)</li>\r\n 	<li>The Science of Wellness (2019 Yale University through Coursera)</li>\r\n</ul>'),(530,545,'_content_with_image_content','field_62237b163420d'),(531,545,'content_with_image_image','383'),(532,545,'_content_with_image_image','field_62237b233420e'),(533,545,'content_with_image',''),(534,545,'_content_with_image','field_62237aec3420c'),(535,545,'logo','491'),(536,545,'_logo','field_6226be311daa9'),(537,545,'rr_content','You can also find me teaching Vinyasa Flow, Fit Flow and several other series at Raw Renewal Yoga.'),(538,545,'_rr_content','field_6226be171daa8'),(539,545,'rr_logo','491'),(540,545,'_rr_logo','field_6226be311daa9'),(541,545,'rr_url',''),(542,545,'_rr_url','field_6226bfe380079'),(543,315,'_wp_attachment_image_alt','Yoga pose in a creek'),(544,493,'content_with_image_right_content','<h3>Find Your Balance</h3>\r\nBring your breath to the movement of your body to experience true balance. Balance is not simply standing on one foot or mastering a hand