-->\n<h3>Importance of Space</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Creating a space for practice is so important.&nbsp; The space allows you to explore your edges and to experiment with your abilities while ensuring that you protected.&nbsp; It is true that you can practice yoga anyway and at anytime with little to no props.&nbsp; Whether you practice on your carpet of your bedroom, your mat in the park or in the most soothing studio surrounded by props and essential oils, yoga will be there for you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Home Studio</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>My home studio provides enough space for 6 - 8 students practicing Hatha, Yin or Vinyasa, 2 students practicing yoga trapeze, or 8 - 10 practicing breathing.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>You can also find me teaching Vinyasa Flow, Fit Flow and several other series at Raw Renewal Yoga.</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":491,\"sizeSlug\":\"thumbnail\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-thumbnail\"><img src=\"http://localhost:10023/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/logo-1-150x150.png\" alt=\"Raw Renewal Yoga logo\" class=\"wp-image-491\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->','About Us','','inherit','closed','closed','','6-revision-v1','','','2022-03-05 00:43:56','2022-03-05 00:43:56','',6,'http://localhost:10023/?p=492',0,'revision','',0),(493,1,'2022-03-05 00:47:01','2022-03-05 00:47:01','','Home','','publish','closed','closed','','home','','','2022-03-08 23:05:20','2022-03-08 23:05:20','',0,'http://localhost:10023/?page_id=493',0,'page','',0),(494,1,'2022-03-05 00:47:01','2022-03-05 00:47:01','<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Since 1993 - Find Your Balance</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Bring your breath to the movement of your body to experience true balance. Balance is not simply standing on one foot or mastering a handstand.  Yoga balance refers to more than your physical practice.  It is the creation of equilibrium in your daily life from eating a balanced diet, to dividing your time between work and play, to giving back as much as you receive and to refrain from greed or overindulgence.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Home','','inherit','closed','closed','','493-revision-v1','','','2022-03-05 00:47:01','2022-03-05 00:47:01','',493,'http://localhost:10023/?p=494',0,'revision','',0),(495,1,'2022-03-05 00:48:56','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Services','','draft','closed','closed','','','','','2022-03-05 00:48:56','2022-03-05 00:48:56','',0,'http://localhost:10023/?page_id=495',0,'page','',0),(496,1,'2022-03-05 00:49:29','2022-03-05 00:49:29','','Blog','','publish','closed','closed','','blog','','','2022-03-05 00:49:29','2022-03-05 00:49:29','',0,'http://localhost:10023/?page_id=496',0,'page','',0),(497,1,'2022-03-05 00:49:29','2022-03-05 00:49:29','','Blog','','inherit','closed','closed','','496-revision-v1','','','2022-03-05 00:49:29','2022-03-05 00:49:29','',496,'http://localhost:10023/?p=497',0,'revision','',0),(498,1,'2022-03-05 00:52:02','2022-03-05 00:52:02','','Contact','','publish','closed','closed','','contact','','','2022-03-05 00:52:02','2022-03-05 00:52:02','',0,'http://localhost:10023/?page_id=498',0,'page','',0),(499,1,'2022-03-05 00:52:02','2022-03-05 00:52:02','','Contact','','inherit','closed','closed','','498-revision-v1','','','2022-03-05 00:52:02','2022-03-05 00:52:02','',498,'http://localhost:10023/?p=499',0,'revision','',0),(500,1,'2022-03-05 00:52:46','2022-03-05 00:52:46','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>No question is unreasonable. &nbsp;Please contact me if you are interested in class or yoga in general. &nbsp;I am always eager to assist.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Can anyone do yoga?</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:parag